name: WhatShouldI
0:
”Alexa, what should I”
”Alexa, ask what should I do”
”Alexa, ask what should I do today”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: what should i
des: This is a non-serious skill for those of us who are indecisive, feeling lazy, or like to procrastinate. Responses from Alexa are a mix of productive activities and short tasks that are mostly meant to get you doing something worthwhile. No prerequisites required.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
